creator: Error300
descriptionHtml:
Can you successfully manage a modern caveman tribe for 10 years? It’s time to prove yourself! Here’s your chance to lead a new caveman tribe and go even further in Welcome to My Cave, a tribe simulation game blending the conveniences of modern life with the Stone Age!

Welcome to My Cave features:
Build your own tribe as you see fit!
Humorous gameplay and silly characters.
Replay options with feature carryover.
Cute and clean modern art with a Stone Age style!
Dozens of buildings to unlock.
descriptionShort: Lead your caveman tribe in Welcome to My Cave, a tribe management simulation
